{"tid":2357999,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育出版社「河蟹」常識書 7.1活動製圖刪遊行剩嘉年華　只問「慶祝活動」不問「民間活動」","createTime":"2021-01-07T23:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T23:45:37.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f291967627765d687ec798a1461064877b54df1","tid":2357999,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MTAjkflLkUWt6hwqN5tpRkujwrI=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JL4NOLOWV5BCNDDIBOJY3UM7VA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMTAjkflLkUWt6hwqN5tpRkujwrI%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJL4NOLOWV5BCNDDIBOJY3UM7VA.jpg&h=c5db0fca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教育出版社《今日常識新領域》小學三年級第6冊，在「香港知多少」部份有關「香港回歸紀念日有哪些活動？」的章節當中，刪除了「香港回歸紀念日活動」中有關七一遊行的製圖及圖下「民間還有甚麼活動？」的思考問題。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n教育出版社《今日常識新領域》小學三年級第6冊，在「香港知多少」部份有關「香港回歸紀念日有哪些活動？」的章節當中，刪除了「香港回歸紀念日活動」中有關七一遊行的製圖及圖下「民間還有甚麼活動？」的思考問題。<br />\n上述內容出自教育出版社《今日常識新領域》小學三年級第6冊，在「香港知多少」部份有關「香港回歸紀念日有哪些活動？」的章節。2019年第三修訂版本提及回歸紀念活動包括嘉年華和遊行，製圖包括市民參與遊行並舉起「改善長者福利」、「爭取勞工權益」、「改善民生」等標語。製圖下問及「除了以上活動外，民間還有甚麼活動？」教師用書版本列明的紅字參考答案亦寫明：「答案合理便可，如遊行和集會。」「參考錦囊」則寫道：「每年的7月1日香港回歸紀念日，香港民間人權陣線等社會運動組織都會舉辦大型遊行，表達對當時政局的不滿」，亦列舉了2003年反對《基本法》23條立法、2013年促請政府實行雙普選和2019年反對《逃犯條例修訂草案》等例子。<br />\n惟《蘋果》翻查最新的2020年重印兼訂正的版本，發現新書刪減了舊版本的遊行製圖，只剩下嘉年華製圖，而有關「民間還有甚麼活動？」的問題亦被刪去，只剩「香港回歸紀念日有哪些慶祝活動？你曾經參加過嗎？」該書其他內容則維持不變。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/RFGVVUZ4CVBCHIKPMQG2UZUZHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FRFGVVUZ4CVBCHIKPMQG2UZUZHA%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z6gSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=9edd379f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FRFGVVUZ4CVBCHIKPMQG2UZUZHA%2F&h=b86aa8aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/RFGVVUZ4CVBCHIKPMQG2UZUZHA/</a>"},{"pid":"26698fa565ec155bdf677f4164a6c463dd46eb00","tid":2357999,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:31:15.000Z","msg":"日本審查歷史教課書：可恥<br />\n香港審查通識教課書：合理"},{"pid":"f4432f71a5800b5486d8dab3c82f67c680465726","tid":2357999,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:45:37.000Z","msg":"全面中共化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190524/640_8687aea9bbbf5844fdfb5ff662a34daa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190524%2F640_8687aea9bbbf5844fdfb5ff662a34daa.jpg&h=ed1b8c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MS1e-gxDRH3_s5bxkU0QdyrtjZY=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XEEVZOD3SVFRFD2UDXIGXMB5CM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMS1e-gxDRH3_s5bxkU0QdyrtjZY%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXEEVZOD3SVFRFD2UDXIGXMB5CM.png&h=ec707f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/640/cpsprodpb/ABD0/production/_103048934_chinataiwanbook_ver6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F640%2Fcpsprodpb%2FABD0%2Fproduction%2F_103048934_chinataiwanbook_ver6.jpg&h=fd346e6c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}